  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.433377223459765        -11.7928          -271.95         -1137.83
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.166402636713781         -4.5280          -104.42          -436.89
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.056366035301508          1.5338            35.37           147.99
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.030515969982431         -0.8304           -19.15           -80.12
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.092108341994549          2.5064            57.80           241.83
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

